Question: Has the boat house door completed its closing sequence yet?
Call: { "func_call": "get_garage_status", "door_id": "garage_boathouse_07", "delay_seconds": 0 }
Response: { "door_id": "garage_boathouse_07", "state": "closing", "timestamp": "2023-11-01T09:50:15Z" }

Question: Set a quick 90-second timer for the south storage door to close.
Call: { "func_call": "set_garage_timer", "door_id": "garage_south_08", "delay_seconds": 90 }
Response: { "door_id": "garage_south_08", "state": "open", "timestamp": "2023-11-01T10:05:42Z" }

